                        <li>Custom searchable multi-select dropdowns</li>
                        <li>Inter font (Google Fonts)</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <h6 class="fw-bold">Database</h6>
                    <ul class="mb-0">
                        <li>SQL Server (planning database)</li>
                        <li>6 Stored Procedures (TRF, PP, Sub TRF, Sub PP, Run All, V3)</li>
                        <li>22 reference/input tables</li>
                        <li>4 output tables (TRF, PP, SUB_TRF, SUB_PP)</li>
